{
  "1118965": "fast-xml-builder attribute quote bypass (GHSA-5wm8-gmm8-39j9) via @aws-sdk/xml-builder->fast-xml-parser->fast-xml-builder@1.1.5. Fix is in fast-xml-builder@1.1.7+ but @aws-sdk/xml-builder (latest) has not yet updated to fast-xml-parser@5.7.3. Attack vector requires controlling XML attribute values passed to the builder; the AWS SDK controls these inputs internally. Remove once AWS SDK updates its fast-xml-parser dependency.",
  "1118966": "fast-xml-builder comment value regex bypass (GHSA-45c6-75p6-83cc) via @aws-sdk/xml-builder->fast-xml-parser->fast-xml-builder@1.1.5. Same dependency chain and upstream fix status as 1118965. Remove once AWS SDK updates its fast-xml-parser dependency.",
  "1119088": "brace-expansion DoS (GHSA-jxxr-4gwj-5jf2) via eslint->minimatch->brace-expansion@5.0.5. Affects dev-only lint tooling; not included in Lambda bundle. Fix in brace-expansion@5.0.6; remove once eslint/typescript-eslint update their minimatch dependency.",
  "1119441": "uuid buffer bounds check (GHSA-w5hq-g745-h8pq) via exceljs->uuid@8.3.2. Only triggered when a buf argument is passed to uuid.v3/v5/v6; ExcelJS controls these calls internally. Remove once exceljs updates its uuid dependency."
}
